<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Password Reset Request</title>
</head>
<body>
  <p>Dear {{ user.firstName }},</p>
  <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account. If you did not make this request, please ignore this email. Otherwise, you can reset your password using the link below:</p>
  <p><a href="{{ url }}">Reset Your Password</a></p>
  <p>For your security, this link will expire in 24 hours. If you encounter any issues or need further assistance, please contact our support team at support@example.com or visit our Help Center.</p>
  <p>Thank you for using our service!</p>
  <p>Best regards,</p>
  <p>Your Support Team</p>
  <p>[Company/Website Name]</p>
</body>
</html>